#: dictee-setup.py:3641 dictee-setup.py:3694
msgid "Enable post-processing (regex rules + dictionary)"
msgstr "Activar posprocesamiento (reglas regex + diccionario)"

#: dictee-setup.py:3655 dictee-setup.py:3708
msgid "Number conversion (text2num)"
msgstr "Conversión de números (text2num)"

#: dictee-setup.py:3658 dictee-setup.py:3711
msgid ""
"Converts spoken numbers to digits.\n"
"Example: \"vingt-trois\" → \"23\""
msgstr ""
"Convierte números hablados en dígitos.\n"
"Ejemplo: \"vingt-trois\" → \"23\""

#: dictee-setup.py:3661 dictee-setup.py:3714
msgid "Auto-capitalization"
msgstr "Capitalización automática"

#: dictee-setup.py:3664 dictee-setup.py:3717
msgid ""
"Capitalizes the first letter after sentence-ending\n"
"punctuation (. ! ?). Parakeet does this natively,\n"
"but post-processing rules may alter the text —\n"
"this ensures correct capitalization afterwards.\n"
"Essential for Vosk/Whisper backends."
msgstr ""
"Pone en mayúscula la primera letra después de la puntuación\n"
"de fin de frase (. ! ?). Parakeet lo hace de forma nativa,\n"
"pero las reglas de post-procesamiento pueden alterar el texto —\n"
"esto asegura la correcta capitalización después.\n"
"Esencial para los backends Vosk/Whisper."

#: dictee-setup.py:3670 dictee-setup.py:3721 dictee-setup.py:3723
#: dictee-setup.py:3774
msgid "Regex rules"
msgstr "Reglas regex"

#: dictee-setup.py:3673 dictee-setup.py:3726
msgid ""
"Applies regex substitution rules to fix\n"
"common ASR errors (voice commands,\n"
"punctuation, formatting)."
msgstr ""
"Aplica reglas de sustitución regex para corregir\n"
"errores ASR comunes (comandos de voz,\n"
"puntuación, formato)."

#: dictee-setup.py:3677 dictee-setup.py:3714 dictee-setup.py:7734
#: dictee-setup.py:3730 dictee-setup.py:3767 dictee-setup.py:7802
msgid "Dictionary"
msgstr "Diccionario"

#: dictee-setup.py:3680 dictee-setup.py:3733
msgid ""
"Replaces words using the dictionary.\n"
"Exact matching on word boundaries."
msgstr ""
"Reemplaza palabras usando el diccionario.\n"
"Coincidencia exacta en los límites de palabra."

#: dictee-setup.py:3683 dictee-setup.py:3728 dictee-setup.py:7678
#: dictee-setup.py:3736 dictee-setup.py:3781 dictee-setup.py:7746
msgid "Continuation"
msgstr "Continuación"

#: dictee-setup.py:3686 dictee-setup.py:3739
msgid ""
"Removes erroneous periods after continuation words\n"
"(articles, prepositions, conjunctions, pronouns, verbs)\n"
"to keep sentences flowing naturally across push-to-talk segments.\n"
"\n"
"Voice command: say your continuation keyword at the start\n"
"of a push to remove the previous punctuation and continue\n"
"in lowercase. The keyword is configurable per language\n"
"in the Continuation tab."
msgstr ""
"Elimina puntos erróneos después de palabras de continuación\n"
"(artículos, preposiciones, conjunciones, pronombres, verbos)\n"
"para mantener las frases fluidas entre segmentos push-to-talk.\n"
"\n"
"Comando de voz: diga su palabra clave de continuación al inicio\n"
"de un push para eliminar la puntuación anterior y continuar\n"
"en minúsculas. La palabra clave es configurable por idioma\n"
"en la pestaña Continuación."

#: dictee-setup.py:3735 dictee-setup.py:3788
msgid "Language rules"
msgstr "Reglas de idioma"

#: dictee-setup.py:3746 dictee-setup.py:3799
msgid "Edit mode"
msgstr "Modo edición"

#: dictee-setup.py:3778 dictee-setup.py:3831
msgid "LLM grammar correction (ollama)"
msgstr "Corrección gramatical LLM (ollama)"

#: dictee-setup.py:3811 dictee-setup.py:3864
msgid "Force CPU (free GPU VRAM)"
msgstr "Forzar CPU (liberar VRAM de GPU)"

#: dictee-setup.py:3816 dictee-setup.py:3869
msgid "~2 GB VRAM with Ministral 3B (+ ~2.5 GB Parakeet)"
msgstr "~2 GB VRAM con Ministral 3B (+ ~2,5 GB Parakeet)"

#: dictee-setup.py:4009 dictee-setup.py:4062
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Language-specific rules (elisions, contractions, typography) applied to the "
"source language only. Currently: <b>{lang}</b>. Only the rules matching your "
"source language will be active."
msgstr ""
"Reglas específicas del idioma (elisiones, contracciones, tipografía) "
"aplicadas solo al idioma de origen. Actualmente: <b>{lang}</b>. Solo las "
"reglas que coincidan con su idioma de origen estarán activas."

#: dictee-setup.py:4021 dictee-setup.py:4074
msgid "Elisions"
msgstr "Elisiones"

#: dictee-setup.py:4024 dictee-setup.py:4077
msgid ""
"Applies French elision rules.\n"
"Example: \"le arbre\" → \"l'arbre\",\n"
"\"de eau\" → \"d'eau\""
msgstr ""
"Aplica reglas de elisión francesas.\n"
"Ejemplo: \"le arbre\" → \"l'arbre\",\n"
"\"de eau\" → \"d'eau\""

#: dictee-setup.py:4028 dictee-setup.py:4081
msgid "Typography (non-breaking spaces)"
msgstr "Tipografía (espacios irrompibles)"

#: dictee-setup.py:4031 dictee-setup.py:4084
msgid ""
"Inserts non-breaking spaces before French\n"
"punctuation marks (: ; ! ? « »)\n"
"as required by French typography rules."
msgstr ""
"Inserta espacios irrompibles antes de los signos\n"
"de puntuación franceses (: ; ! ? « »)\n"
"según las reglas tipográficas francesas."

#: dictee-setup.py:4041 dictee-setup.py:4094
msgid ""
"No specific rules needed. Contractions (don't, I'm, can't) are handled "
"natively by the ASR engine."
msgstr ""
"No se necesitan reglas específicas. Las contracciones (don't, I'm, can't) se "
"gestionan de forma nativa por el motor ASR."

#: dictee-setup.py:4052 dictee-setup.py:4105
msgid "Elisions & contractions"
msgstr "Elisiones y contracciones"

#: dictee-setup.py:4055 dictee-setup.py:4108
msgid ""
"Italian elisions and prepositional contractions.\n"
"Elisions: \"lo uomo\" → \"l'uomo\", \"di accordo\" → \"d'accordo\"\n"
"Contractions: \"di il\" → \"del\", \"a la\" → \"alla\",\n"
"\"in il\" → \"nel\", \"su la\" → \"sulla\""
msgstr ""
"Elisiones y contracciones preposicionales italianas.\n"
"Elisiones: \"lo uomo\" → \"l'uomo\", \"di accordo\" → \"d'accordo\"\n"
"Contracciones: \"di il\" → \"del\", \"a la\" → \"alla\",\n"
"\"in il\" → \"nel\", \"su la\" → \"sulla\""

#: dictee-setup.py:4067 dictee-setup.py:4120
msgid "Contractions & inverted punctuation"
msgstr "Contracciones y puntuación invertida"

#: dictee-setup.py:4070 dictee-setup.py:4123
msgid ""
"Spanish contractions and inverted punctuation.\n"
"Contractions: \"a el\" → \"al\", \"de el\" → \"del\"\n"
"Punctuation: adds ¿ before questions and ¡ before exclamations."
msgstr ""
"Contracciones y puntuación invertida españolas.\n"
"Contracciones: \"a el\" → \"al\", \"de el\" → \"del\"\n"
"Puntuación: añade ¿ antes de preguntas y ¡ antes de exclamaciones."

#: dictee-setup.py:4081 dictee-setup.py:4110 dictee-setup.py:4134
#: dictee-setup.py:4163
msgid "Contractions"
msgstr "Contracciones"

#: dictee-setup.py:4084 dictee-setup.py:4137
msgid ""
"Portuguese fused contractions.\n"
"\"de o\" → \"do\", \"em a\" → \"na\", \"por os\" → \"pelos\",\n"
"\"de este\" → \"deste\", \"em ele\" → \"nele\""
msgstr ""
"Contracciones fusionadas portuguesas.\n"
"\"de o\" → \"do\", \"em a\" → \"na\", \"por os\" → \"pelos\",\n"
"\"de este\" → \"deste\", \"em ele\" → \"nele\""

#: dictee-setup.py:4095 dictee-setup.py:4124 dictee-setup.py:4148
#: dictee-setup.py:4177
msgid "Contractions & typography"
msgstr "Contracciones y tipografía"

#: dictee-setup.py:4098 dictee-setup.py:4151
msgid ""
"German contractions and typography.\n"
"Contractions: \"an dem\" → \"am\", \"in dem\" → \"im\",\n"
"\"zu dem\" → \"zum\", \"zu der\" → \"zur\"\n"
"Typography: \"text\" → \\u201etext\\u201c (German quotes)"
msgstr ""
"Contracciones y tipografía alemanas.\n"
"Contracciones: \"an dem\" → \"am\", \"in dem\" → \"im\",\n"
"\"zu dem\" → \"zum\", \"zu der\" → \"zur\"\n"
"Tipografía: \"text\" → \\u201etext\\u201c (comillas alemanas)"

#: dictee-setup.py:4113 dictee-setup.py:4166
msgid ""
"Dutch contractions and time expressions.\n"
"\"het\" → \"'t\", \"een\" → \"'n\"\n"
"\"in de morgens\" → \"'s morgens\""
msgstr ""
"Contracciones y expresiones temporales neerlandesas.\n"
